high_descs: Turn right, go across the room and face the shelves on the right.
Pick up the vase next to the statue on the shelf.
Turn right around and go to the coffee table.
Put the vase to the left of the newspaper on the coffee table.
Turn left and go to the black table in the corner.
Pick up the blue vase on the black table.
Turn around and go back to the coffee table.
Put the blue vase between the newspapers on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put two vases on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right, walk straight, turn right to the table
Pick up the glass jar on the table
Turn right, walk straight, turn right to the glass table
Put the glass jar on the table
Turn left, walk straight, turn right to the desk with the lamp
Pick up the blue plate on the desk
Turn right, turn right, walk straight, turn left to the glass table
Put the blue plate on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a jar and plate on a table

high_descs: Turn right and walk then head right again to the corner table.
Grab the bowl from the table.
Turn around and walk to the small table in the middle of the room.
Place the bowl on the table.
Turn left and walk to the stand with the lamp on it.
Grab the blue disc from the stand.
Turn around and walk to the table in the middle of the room.
Place the blue disc on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place two objects on two different tables.
